{"type":"message","id":"e53abca0","parentId":"06eb0a63","timestamp":"2026-05-23T01:40:11.589Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user says \"昨天你分析的那个\" - they are referring to something I analyzed yesterday. They say \"你看啊看\" which means \"look into it\" - they're pointing me to the message they quoted (reply_to).\n\nThe quoted message ID is `om_x100b6e3320efb0a0b287880c4cfee27`. Let me try fetching the actual message they were replying to by using this message ID with the get_thread_messages call.\n\nActually, the thread_id parameter might need to be the actual thread ID, not the message ID. But let me try - it seems like the message_id format in feishu might be `om_` prefix for messages.\n\nActually wait - the user said \"昨天你分析的那个\" and quoted a message. The quoted message was `om_x100b6e3320efb0a0b287880c4cfee27`. This might be the message from yesterday that they're referring to. But it's in a thread context.\n\nLet me look for the session from yesterday to find the conversation. The main session is quite long and started before yesterday. Let me try to get the feishu messages from today and see if I can get context that way.\n\nActually, the issue might be that I need to try allConversations to find the context. But actually, the current conversation IS the same one. Let me look more carefully at the quoted message's thread.\n\nActually the user's message is a reply to `om_x100b6e3320efb0a0b287880c4cfee27`. This is a message ID. Let me try to fetch this message directly using the search messages tool.\n","thinkingSignature":"244d9b83a7f14fcb7a9aea6ed9f1ab69589cf79d49cd8d7220d1f729c529dc79"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ifs8ya5ixmf6_1","name":"feishu_im_user_search_messages","arguments":{"page_size":20,"query":"选品大师 发消息","relative_time":"last_2_days"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":119,"output":405,"cacheRead":58114,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":58638,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779500400074,"responseId":"06603870ce243cbf37effde283702540"}}
{"type":"message","id":"9896fd2c","parentId":"e53abca0","timestamp":"2026-05-23T01:40:14.405Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_ifs8ya5ixmf6_1","toolName":"feishu_im_user_search_messages","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"messages\": [\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b6e309728c8a8b2c2fd791a14da7\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"interactive\",\n      \"content\": \"<card>\\n收到了。你现在是在和我（KIIT）说话，而 TK 选品大师那边还是没回应对吗？\\n\\n关键问题需要确认一下：**你现在给 TK 选品大师发消息，是在哪个对话里点的？**\\n\\n是在飞书里直接找到「TK 选品大师」这个机器人的对话窗口发的，还是在别的什么地方？\\n\\n因为从日志看，你发给我的这两条消息（20:32 和 20:34）都是走的 `feishu[kiit]` 账号处理，不是 `tts`。这说明**TK 选品大师的机器人可能根本没收到你的消息**，或者你发错地方了。\\n</card>\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"cli_a93650c6fc785bce\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"app\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-05-22T20:35:42+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": true,\n      \"reply_to\": \"om_x100b6e308c06d0acc2deb3935c80faa\",\n      \"chat_id\": \"oc_891331ffe537b34aa96f0be8874885c8\",\n      \"chat_type\": \"p2p\",\n      \"chat_partner\": {\n        \"open_id\": \"ou_11f95142ee4622f42acc029c870f68bb\"\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b6e34a1b6b960b4cb0da7be6e6e1\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"interactive\",\n      \"content\": \"<card>\\nTK 选品大师的账号 allowFrom 白名单只授权了另一个用户，**没有包含你的 open_id**（`ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb`），所以它的飞书账号收不到你的消息。\\n\\n已修复 ✅ 重新配置了白名单。\\n\\n建议等 1 分钟让配置生效，然后再给 TK 选品大师 发消息试试。如果还有问题我们再排查。\\n\\n⚠️ 🔌 Gateway: channels.feishu.accounts.tts failed\\n</card>\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"cli_a93650c6fc785bce\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"app\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-05-22T16:08:24+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": true,\n      \"reply_to\": \"om_x100b6e34a0420114c23528d3a64f5ed\",\n      \"chat_id\": \"oc_891331ffe537b34aa96f0be8874885c8\",\n      \"chat_type\": \"p2p\",\n      \"chat_partner\": {\n        \"open_id\": \"ou_11f95142ee4622f42acc029c870f68bb\"\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b6e24047130a8b3605541f449898\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"interactive\",\n      \"content\": \"<card>\\n5.20版本我记下来了。选品大师发消息有问题——能具体说说是什么情况吗？比如：\\n- 发不出去？报什么错？\\n- 发错了内容？\\n- 发给错误的人？\\n- 或者其他现象？说清楚现象我帮你排查。\\n</card>\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"cli_a93650c6fc785bce\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"app\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-05-23T09:36:44+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": true,\n      \"reply_to\": \"om_x100b6e240747bca8c3c87380af53fcd\",\n      \"chat_id\": \"oc_891331ffe537b34aa96f0be8874885c8\",\n      \"chat_type\": \"p2p\",\n      \"chat_partner\": {\n        \"open_id\": \"ou_11f95142ee4622f42acc029c870f68bb\"\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b6e240747bca8c3c87380af53fcd\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"text\",\n      \"content\": \"5.20这个版本还行，但是我最常用的 选品大师发消息有问题，这就让我有点恼火。 有修复办法吗\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"user\",\n        \"name\": \"HALEI\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-05-23T09:36:24+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": false,\n      \"chat_id\": \"oc_891331ffe537b34aa96f0be8874885c8\",\n      \"chat_type\": \"p2p\",\n      \"chat_partner\": {\n        \"open_id\": \"ou_11f95142ee4622f42acc029c870f68bb\"\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b6e31015c5100b4a130711338f03\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"interactive\",\n      \"content\": \"<card>\\n好的，既然 ID 信息都对，那问题可能不在配置，而在**飞书消息的路由**上。\\n\\n你看一下这个场景是不是你现在的状态：\\n\\n**你在飞书里给 TK 选品大师 发消息 → 消息走到 **`Feishu[default]`** → 没有回复**\\n\\n同时你确认过：\\n- TK 选品大师 的 app_id (`cli_a930f78f51399bc6`) 是对的\\n- web UI 后台和 tts 通讯正常如果是这样，问题很可能是：**TK 选品大师 这个 bot 在飞书里被加错了，或者 bot 的消息接收配置有问题**。\\n\\n我需要你确认一件事：\\n\\n**你现在在飞书里，能不能看到 TK 选品大师 这个 bot 的对话窗口？能的话，帮我确认一下这个 bot 在飞书里的 app_id 是不是 **`cli_a930f78f51399bc6`**？**\\n\\n（你之前说看了后台绑定的 cli id 是对的，我理解你说的是 OpenClaw 里的配置也是对的。那飞书那边 TK bot 本身的 app_id 对不对？）\\n\\n如果飞书里 TK bot 的 app_id 和 OpenClaw 里配置的不一致（比如是另一个 app），那就是根本原因。\\n</card>\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"cli_a93650c6fc785bce\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"app\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-05-22T21:07:05+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": true,\n      \"reply_to\": \"om_x100b6e31004090a0c2a6de25c25f61c\",\n      \"chat_id\": \"oc_891331ffe537b34aa96f0be8874885c8\",\n      \"chat_type\": \"p2p\",\n      \"chat_partner\": {\n        \"open_id\": \"ou_11f95142ee4622f42acc029c870f68bb\"\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b6e3106ee48b0b3eb063cbf0181e\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"interactive\",\n      \"content\": \"<card>\\n等等，你是说：\\n- 在 **web UI 后台**你和 tts 通讯正常 ✓\\n- 你查了绑定的 cli id 也是对的 ✓\\n- 但在 **飞书 app 里**发消息给 TK 选品大师，没有回复 ✗如果是这样，说明 **tts 账号本身是正常的**，问题出在**飞书消息没送到 tts**——消息走到 `Feishu[default]` 去了。\\n\\n让我问你几个关键问题确认一下：\\n1. **你在飞书里给 TK 选品大师发消息**，你是怎么找到这个机器人的？是在飞书里搜索名字加的联系人，还是从某个链接/card 点进去的？\\n2. **你点进去的 TK 选品大师 对话框**，它的头像/名字显示的是什么？能不能截个图给我看看？\\n3. **这个机器人的 app_id 是 **`cli_a930f78f51399bc6`，你能帮我确认一下你在飞书里加的这个 bot 的 app_id 也是这个吗？因为之前日志显示你发的消息全部走的是 `Feishu[default]`，说明你加的 bot 联系人可能不是 tts 这个账号，而是另一个。\\n</card>\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"cli_a93650c6fc785bce\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"app\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-05-22T21:05:06+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": true,\n      \"reply_to\": \"om_x100b6e31087baca4c4ac0bb621d7f67\",\n      \"chat_id\": \"oc_891331ffe537b34aa96f0be8874885c8\",\n      \"chat_type\": \"p2p\",\n      \"chat_partner\": {\n        \"open_id\": \"ou_11f95142ee4622f42acc029c870f68bb\"\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b6e3165a6eca8b2890c79568d780\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"interactive\",\n      \"content\": \"<card>\\n抱歉，我只能 spawn \\\"main\\\" agent 的子会话，tts agent 不在这个主会话的控制范围内，所以没法直接给它发消息。\\n\\n不过我刚注意到一个关键点——你说在后台查 tts 会话。请查一下 TK 选品大师 bot（app: `cli_a930f78f51399bc6`）在飞书后台的状态：\\n1. 这个应用是**启用**还是**停用**状态？\\n2. 应用的**消息接收模式**是什么？（Webhook 还是长连接）\\n3. 有没有**事件订阅**配置？如果这个应用在飞书后台被停用或删除了，那就解释了为什么消息全部走到 `Feishu[default]` 而不是 `Feishu[tts]`——因为 tts bot 根本不存在或不可用了。\\n\\n你查一下告诉我，我再确认下一步怎么排查。\\n</card>\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"cli_a93650c6fc785bce\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"app\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-05-22T20:57:27+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": true,\n      \"reply_to\": \"om_x100b6e3164b344acc2643072f1ee4c4\",\n      \"chat_id\": \"oc_891331ffe537b34aa96f0be8874885c8\",\n      \"chat_type\": \"p2p\",\n      \"chat_partner\": {\n        \"open_id\": \"ou_11f95142ee4622f42acc029c870f68bb\"\n      }\n    }\n  ],\n  \"has_more\": false\n}"}],"details":{"messages":[{"message_id":"om_x100b6e309728c8a8b2c2fd791a14da7","msg_type":"interactive","content":"<card>\n收到了。你现在是在和我（KIIT）说话，而 TK 选品大师那边还是没回应对吗？\n\n关键问题需要确认一下：**你现在给 TK 选品大师发消息，是在哪个对话里点的？**\n\n是在飞书里直接找到「TK 选品大师」这个机器人的对话窗口发的，还是在别的什么地方？\n\n因为从日志看，你发给我的这两条消息（20:32 和 20:34）都是走的 `feishu[kiit]` 账号处理，不是 `tts`。这说明**TK 选品大师的机器人可能根本没收到你的消息**，或者你发错地方了。\n</card>","sender":{"id":"cli_a93650c6fc785bce","sender_type":"app"},"create_time":"2026-05-22T20:35:42+08:00","deleted":false,"updated":true,"reply_to":"om_x100b6e308c06d0acc2deb3935c80faa","chat_id":"oc_891331ffe537b34aa96f0be8874885c8","chat_type":"p2p","chat_partner":{"open_id":"ou_11f95142ee4622f42acc029c870f68bb"}},{"message_id":"om_x100b6e34a1b6b960b4cb0da7be6e6e1","msg_type":"interactive","content":"<card>\nTK 选品大师的账号 allowFrom 白名单只授权了另一个用户，**没有包含你的 open_id**（`ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb`），所以它的飞书账号收不到你的消息。\n\n已修复 ✅ 重新配置了白名单。\n\n建议等 1 分钟让配置生效，然后再给 TK 选品大师 发消息试试。如果还有问题我们再排查。\n\n⚠️ 🔌 Gateway: channels.feishu.accounts.tts failed\n</card>","sender":{"id":"cli_a93650c6fc785bce","sender_type":"app"},"create_time":"2026-05-22T16:08:24+08:00","deleted":false,"updated":true,"reply_to":"om_x100b6e34a0420114c23528d3a64f5ed","chat_id":"oc_891331ffe537b34aa96f0be8874885c8","chat_type":"p2p","chat_partner":{"open_id":"ou_11f95142ee4622f42acc029c870f68bb"}},{"message_id":"om_x100b6e24047130a8b3605541f449898","msg_type":"interactive","content":"<card>\n5.20版本我记下来了。选品大师发消息有问题——能具体说说是什么情况吗？比如：\n- 发不出去？报什么错？\n- 发错了内容？\n- 发给错误的人？\n- 或者其他现象？说清楚现象我帮你排查。\n</card>","sender":{"id":"cli_a93650c6fc785bce","sender_type":"app"},"create_time":"2026-05-23T09:36:44+08:00","deleted":false,"updated":true,"reply_to":"om_x100b6e240747bca8c3c87380af53fcd","chat_id":"oc_891331ffe537b34aa96f0be8874885c8","chat_type":"p2p","chat_partner":{"open_id":"ou_11f95142ee4622f42acc029c870f68bb"}},{"message_id":"om_x100b6e240747bca8c3c87380af53fcd","msg_type":"text","content":"5.20这个版本还行，但是我最常用的 选品大师发消息有问题，这就让我有点恼火。 有修复办法吗","sender":{"id":"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb","sender_type":"user","name":"HALEI"},"create_time":"2026-05-23T09:36:24+08:00","deleted":false,"updated":false,"chat_id":"oc_891331ffe537b34aa96f0be8874885c8","chat_type":"p2p","chat_partner":{"open_id":"ou_11f95142ee4622f42acc029c870f68bb"}},{"message_id":"om_x100b6e31015c5100b4a130711338f03","msg_type":"interactive","content":"<card>\n好的，既然 ID 信息都对，那问题可能不在配置，而在**飞书消息的路由**上。\n\n你看一下这个场景是不是你现在的状态：\n\n**你在飞书里给 TK 选品大师 发消息 → 消息走到 **`Feishu[default]`** → 没有回复**\n\n同时你确认过：\n- TK 选品大师 的 app_id (`cli_a930f78f51399bc6`) 是对的\n- web UI 后台和 tts 通讯正常如果是这样，问题很可能是：**TK 选品大师 这个 bot 在飞书里被加错了，或者 bot 的消息接收配置有问题**。\n\n我需要你确认一件事：\n\n**你现在在飞书里，能不能看到 TK 选品大师 这个 bot 的对话窗口？能的话，帮我确认一下这个 bot 在飞书里的 app_id 是不是 **`cli_a930f78f51399bc6`**？**\n\n（你之前说看了后台绑定的 cli id 是对的，我理解你说的是 OpenClaw 里的配置也是对的。那飞书那边 TK bot 本身的 app_id 对不对？）\n\n如果飞书里 TK bot 的 app_id 和 OpenClaw 里配置的不一致（比如是另一个 app），那就是根本原因。\n</card>","sender":{"id":"cli_a93650c6fc785bce","sender_type":"app"},"create_time":"2026-05-22T21:07:05+08:00","deleted":false,"updated":true,"reply_to":"om_x100b6e31004090a0c2a6de25c25f61c","chat_id":"oc_891331ffe537b34aa96f0be8874885c8","chat_type":"p2p","chat_partner":{"open_id":"ou_11f95142ee4622f42acc029c870f68bb"}},{"message_id":"om_x100b6e3106ee48b0b3eb063cbf0181e","msg_type":"interactive","content":"<card>\n等等，你是说：\n- 在 **web UI 后台**你和 tts 通讯正常 ✓\n- 你查了绑定的 cli id 也是对的 ✓\n- 但在 **飞书 app 里**发消息给 TK 选品大师，没有回复 ✗如果是这样，说明 **tts 账号本身是正常的**，问题出在**飞书消息没送到 tts**——消息走到 `Feishu[default]` 去了。\n\n让我问你几个关键问题确认一下：\n1. **你在飞书里给 TK 选品大师发消息**，你是怎么找到这个机器人的？是在飞书里搜索名字加的联系人，还是从某个链接/card 点进去的？\n2. **你点进去的 TK 选品大师 对话框**，它的头像/名字显示的是什么？能不能截个图给我看看？\n3. **这个机器人的 app_id 是 **`cli_a930f78f51399bc6`，你能帮我确认一下你在飞书里加的这个 bot 的 app_id 也是这个吗？因为之前日志显示你发的消息全部走的是 `Feishu[default]`，说明你加的 bot 联系人可能不是 tts 这个账号，而是另一个。\n</card>","sender":{"id":"cli_a93650c6fc785bce","sender_type":"app"},"create_time":"2026-05-22T21:05:06+08:00","deleted":false,"updated":true,"reply_to":"om_x100b6e31087baca4c4ac0bb621d7f67","chat_id":"oc_891331ffe537b34aa96f0be8874885c8","chat_type":"p2p","chat_partner":{"open_id":"ou_11f95142ee4622f42acc029c870f68bb"}},{"message_id":"om_x100b6e3165a6eca8b2890c79568d780","msg_type":"interactive","content":"<card>\n抱歉，我只能 spawn \"main\" agent 的子会话，tts agent 不在这个主会话的控制范围内，所以没法直接给它发消息。\n\n不过我刚注意到一个关键点——你说在后台查 tts 会话。请查一下 TK 选品大师 bot（app: `cli_a930f78f51399bc6`）在飞书后台的状态：\n1. 这个应用是**启用**还是**停用**状态？\n2. 应用的**消息接收模式**是什么？（Webhook 还是长连接）\n3. 有没有**事件订阅**配置？如果这个应用在飞书后台被停用或删除了，那就解释了为什么消息全部走到 `Feishu[default]` 而不是 `Feishu[tts]`——因为 tts bot 根本不存在或不可用了。\n\n你查一下告诉我，我再确认下一步怎么排查。\n</card>","sender":{"id":"cli_a93650c6fc785bce","sender_type":"app"},"create_time":"2026-05-22T20:57:27+08:00","deleted":false,"updated":true,"reply_to":"om_x100b6e3164b344acc2643072f1ee4c4","chat_id":"oc_891331ffe537b34aa96f0be8874885c8","chat_type":"p2p","chat_partner":{"open_id":"ou_11f95142ee4622f42acc029c870f68bb"}}],"has_more":false},"isError":false,"timestamp":1779500414388}}
{"type":"message","id":"449e542d","parentId":"9896fd2c","timestamp":"2026-05-23T01:40:30.414Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I see what happened yesterday. Let me look at the full conversation context. From the messages:\n\n1. The user reported that 5.20 version has an issue where the \"选品大师\" (TK product selector agent) doesn't respond to messages\n2. The KIIT bot (Feishu[default]) investigated and found that the tts account's allowFrom whitelist didn't include the user's open_id\n3. A fix was applied: `✅ 重新配置了白名单。` but there was also a warning: `⚠️ 🔌 Gateway: channels.feishu.accounts.tts failed`\n4. Then further troubleshooting happened but it seems the issue might not have been fully resolved\n\nThe key issues identified:\n- The tts account's allowFrom whitelist was fixed to include the user's open_id\n- But there was a Gateway error: `channels.feishu.accounts.tts failed`\n\nLet me check the current status of the tts account configuration and see if the gateway error is still present.\n","thinkingSignature":"925048ae49894e067d62f98fa9075c117004e20af4047dd4f355b2b6c8403f55"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n看到了。昨天的问题分析是：\n\n1. **TK 选品大师（tts）的 allowFrom 白名单没有包含你的 open_id**，导致你的消息全部走到 `Feishu[default]` 而不是 tts\n2. 当时修复了白名单，但最后有个警告：`⚠️ 🔌 Gateway: channels.feishu.accounts.tts failed`\n\n让我检查一下当前配置和这个错误：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_aeov2e1dhgax_1","name":"gateway","arguments":{"action":"config.schema.lookup","path":"channels.feishu.accounts.tts"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_aeov2e1dhgax_2","name":"gateway","arguments":{"action":"config.get"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":2627,"output":355,"cacheRead":58230,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":61212,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779500414450,"responseId":"0660387ed55eaa4e40c386a89b455379"}}
