{"type":"message","id":"7bc9de19","parentId":"13cb9886","timestamp":"2026-05-23T01:42:08.432Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I see the problem clearly:\n\n1. **Top-level feishu config** (which applies to all accounts unless overridden):\n   - `allowFrom: [\"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\"]` ✅\n   - `dmPolicy: allowlist` ✅\n\n2. **tts account specific config**:\n   - `allowFrom: NOT SET` → inherits from top-level ✅\n   - `dmPolicy: NOT SET` → inherits from top-level ✅\n\nSo the tts account should be receiving messages from `ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb`. The config looks fine.\n\nBut yesterday there was an error: `⚠️ 🔌 Gateway: channels.feishu.accounts.tts failed`\n\nAnd from the search results, the issue was described as:\n- \"TK 选品大师的账号 allowFrom 白名单只授权了另一个用户，**没有包含你的 open_id**（`ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb`），所以它的飞书账号收不到你的消息。\"\n- \"已修复 ✅ 重新配置了白名单。\"\n\nSo it was already fixed yesterday. But now HALEI is saying it still has problems in 5.20 version.\n\nWait - looking at the message more carefully:\n\nThe user is referencing \"昨天你分析的那个\" - so yesterday there was a discussion. And the search results show the problem was with the allowFrom for tts being fixed yesterday.\n\nBut the user says \"5.20这个版本还行，但是我最常用的 选品大师发消息有问题，这就让我有点恼火。 有修复办法吗\"\n\nNow in 5.20, they're saying the problem still exists. But based on the config I just checked, the allowFrom IS properly set to include `ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb`.\n\n\nThe config appears correct, yet the user is reporting the issue persists in 5.20. I should verify whether the Gateway is actually processing messages for the tts account or if something else is failing. There's also that error from yesterday about the tts account failing, which might be relevant to what's happening now.\n\nLet me check if there are any logs showing what exactly is broken.\n","thinkingSignature":"8e19533afcaca9d6d36815f8ba692d469bc3d36c7660875ab0c4ff87712b584b"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_fxeid4mebvtn_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"journalctl -n 100 --no-pager 2>/dev/null | grep -i \"feishu\\|tts\\|account\" | tail -30","timeout":5}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_fxeid4mebvtn_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"find /home/halei/.openclaw/logs -name \"*.log\" -mtime -1 2>/dev/null | head -5","timeout":5}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":340,"output":609,"cacheRead":68257,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":69206,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779500518440,"responseId":"066038e7c15cdc91a0b84ed87127e886"}}
