{"type":"message","id":"0598a8ef","parentId":"d79c625a","timestamp":"2026-05-23T02:11:29.693Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户问\"修复了吗\"，我之前在分析选品大师发消息的问题。让我快速检查一下配置和当前状态。\n\n从之前的分析来看，tts账号（TK选品大师）的配置问题：\n1. tts account没有设置allowFrom，而top-level（kiit账号所在）设置了allowFrom包含用户open_id\n2. 但tts是独立账号，它继承的是default account的dmPolicy=\"pairing\"，而不是top-level的allowlist\n\n问题是：tts账号没有allowFrom配置，所以它可能无法正确接收用户的消息。\n\n让我检查一下当前配置是否有变化，以及是否需要给tts账号添加allowFrom。\n","thinkingSignature":"cf866cec763c2d8f23754fac4d1585bdf67caaa48316d4ba7e1d235d669089b9"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n让我快速检查一下当前状态：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ln9wl0qiw70e_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 -c \"\nimport json\nwith open('/home/halei/.openclaw/openclaw.json') as f:\n    cfg = json.load(f)\ntts = cfg['channels']['feishu']['accounts']['tts']\nprint('tts account 配置:')\nfor k in ['enabled','allowFrom','dmPolicy','appId']:\n    print(f'  {k}: {tts.get(k, \\\"未设置\\\")}')\nprint()\nkiit = cfg['channels']['feishu']['accounts']['kiit']\nprint('kiit account 配置:')\nfor k in ['enabled','allowFrom','dmPolicy']:\n    print(f'  {k}: {kiit.get(k, \\\"未设置\\\")}')\n\"","timeout":5}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":77141,"output":322,"cacheRead":1551,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":79014,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779502276141,"responseId":"06603fc4dc527a004ca84df80c87bb9a"}}
