{"type":"message","id":"650448da","parentId":"f2f49171","timestamp":"2026-05-23T11:55:23.176Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_3sx2u4rly8si_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"description\": \"选品专家 Agent - 负责产品筛选、市场调研、竞品分析、选品策略制定\",\n  \"capabilities\": [\n    \"市场潜力评估\",\n    \"竞品分析\",\n    \"产品筛选\",\n    \"数据驱动选品\"\n  ],\n  \"model\": \"gemini/gemini-2.0-flash\",\n  \"workspaceDir\": \"/home/halei/.openclaw/workspace/Selector\",\n  \"tools\": {\n    \"allow\": [\n      \"cron\",\n      \"read\",\n      \"write\",\n      \"edit\",\n      \"apply_patch\",\n      \"memory_search\",\n      \"memory_get\",\n      \"browser\",\n      \"message\",\n      \"exec\",\n      \"web_search\",\n      \"web_fetch\"\n    ]\n  },\n  \"createdAt\": \"2026-03-27T19:45:00+08:00\"\n}"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":38,"aggregated":"{\n  \"description\": \"选品专家 Agent - 负责产品筛选、市场调研、竞品分析、选品策略制定\",\n  \"capabilities\": [\n    \"市场潜力评估\",\n    \"竞品分析\",\n    \"产品筛选\",\n    \"数据驱动选品\"\n  ],\n  \"model\": \"gemini/gemini-2.0-flash\",\n  \"workspaceDir\": \"/home/halei/.openclaw/workspace/Selector\",\n  \"tools\": {\n    \"allow\": [\n      \"cron\",\n      \"read\",\n      \"write\",\n      \"edit\",\n      \"apply_patch\",\n      \"memory_search\",\n      \"memory_get\",\n      \"browser\",\n      \"message\",\n      \"exec\",\n      \"web_search\",\n      \"web_fetch\"\n    ]\n  },\n  \"createdAt\": \"2026-03-27T19:45:00+08:00\"\n}","cwd":"/home/halei/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1779537323174}}
{"type":"message","id":"67392a5c","parentId":"650448da","timestamp":"2026-05-23T11:55:57.025Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The tts agent config uses `gemini/gemini-2.0-flash` but the global config says it should use `minimax/MiniMax-M2.7`. Let me check what agents list says in openclaw.json.\n\nActually, let me think about this differently. The user is saying \"still not working\". The core issue is likely that when the user sends a message to the TK 选品大师 bot in Feishu, the message is being routed to kiit instead of tts. \n\nLet me think about the routing logic. In Feishu, each bot has its own app with a unique app_id. When a user sends a message to a specific bot, Feishu delivers that message to the webhook endpoint for that specific app. \n\nThe question is: does OpenClaw handle multi-account routing correctly? When Feishu delivers a message to `cli_a930f78f51399bc6` (tts), does OpenClaw know to route it to the tts agent?\n\nActually, I think I found the key issue. Look at the search results from earlier - the messages from yesterday show the user asking \"5.20这个版本还行，但是我最常用的 选品大师发消息有问题，这就让我有点恼火。 有修复办法吗\". \n\nThese messages went to the kiit bot, not the tts bot. But the user's original message was to the TK 选品大师 bot with app_id `cli_a930f78f51399bc6`. Yet those messages appeared in the kiit conversation. This means the message routing is broken at the Feishu level OR at the OpenClaw level.\n\nWait - actually when I look at the search result, the chat_partner is `ou_11f95142ee4622f42acc029c870f68bb`. Let me check this. Earlier when I searched messages and got:\n\nThe messages show `\"chat_partner\": {\"open_id\": \"ou_11f95142ee4622f42acc029c870f68bb\"}` - this isn't the user's open_id. The user's open_id is `ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb`. So the messages shown might actually be the bot (KIIT) sending messages to another user, not the user messaging the bot. \n\nSo actually, the message routing might be correct but I need to understand the real problem better. I don't have the full conversation from yesterday, just fragments from search. Let me think about what could be happening and maybe try a more direct approach to diagnosing the issue.\n\nActually, I think there's a simpler question I should ask - I should ask the user to confirm exactly which bot they're messaging. The TK 选品大师 bot should have its own conversation window in Feishu. The user should confirm they're clicking on the right bot. But I don't want to just ask - I should try to help. \n\nLet me think about another approach. The core problem is that the tts account's messages are being received (cron runs fine at 9AM) but when the user sends a direct message to the TK bot in Feishu, it doesn't respond. After our fix to add allowFrom/dmPolicy, it still doesn't work. Let me check if the tts account has a persistent session that could be blocking new messages. Also, I want to verify if the user might be sending messages to the kiit bot by mistake, even though they're trying to reach tts. Actually, when I search messages from the user in the last 2 days, I only see the messages at 09:36 - those from today. The user sent a message at 09:36 today to kiit saying \"5.20这个版本还行\", and then another at 09:39 saying \"昨天你分析的那个，你看啊看\". But there's no new message to tts after our fix. So the user hasn't actually tested sending a message to tts yet - they're just telling me it still doesn't work from our earlier conversation.\n\nThe real question is: has the user tried sending a NEW message to TK 选品大师 after the fix? It doesn't seem like they have. I should ask them to do that first.\n\nBut also, I need to think about the earlier finding - when I searched for messages about 选品大师, I found one that was a card from kiit bot to `ou_11f95142ee4622f42acc029c870f68bb` at 20:35:42 on May 22. This suggests the kiit bot is sending cards to someone - this might be a response to a user who was testing the bot. But the user's open_id is `ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb` so these are different people. I need to understand the context better.\n\nWait, I think I've been misunderstanding the architecture. Let me reconsider how OpenClaw's multi-account Feishu integration actually works. When a user sends a message to TK 选品大师 in Feishu, the message goes to the TK bot app, and OpenClaw should receive it via webhook, look up the account mapping based on the message's app_id, find the associated agent (tts), and deliver the message. If our config now has the allowFrom and dmPolicy set correctly, it should work. But maybe there's a webhook endpoint issue - maybe all accounts are using the same webhook path like `/feishu/events` and the app_id is what determines which account processes it, so it should be routed correctly.\n\nOr perhaps the issue is with how the webhook is registered - if the user created a \"custom bot\" in Feishu rather than using the official Marketplace app, it might not support the same bot profile features. I should ask the user directly what specific error or behavior they're seeing when they try to message TK 选品大师, and also ask them to try sending a new test message to the bot.\n\nI also need to verify whether tkinter's bot token has the necessary messaging permissions in Feishu's app console, and then check if there's an active session for tts that could be blocking new incoming messages.\n","thinkingSignature":"175ec0f6e51a92c86a4aceab2371ffdf9fd4941c87618d8526c77ba81c15c774"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n还没测新消息呢——你刚才发给我的还是kiit这边的对话。我需要确认几件事：\n\n**1. 你现在在飞书里，是直接在 TK 选品大师 的bot窗口发消息吗？**\n\nTK 选品大师的飞书 app_id 是 `cli_a930f78f51399bc6`，你发消息的那个对话框里，点开 bot 头像或信息，确认一下是这个 app_id 的 bot。\n\n**2. 昨天你说发消息给 TK 选品大师没有回复——具体表现是什么？**\n\n- 消息发出去显示\"已送达\"但没有回复？\n- 还是消息压根发不出去（报错了）？\n- 还是消息发到了我（kiit）这边？\n\n**3. 现在这个bot还在跑吗？**\n\nTK 选品大师上次跑是今天早上9点 cron 触发。从 sessions 目录看，tts 最后活跃时间是 `2026-05-23T01:02`（约早上9点），之后没有新的用户消息会话。\n\n帮我确认一下以上三点，我再决定怎么修。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":255,"output":1502,"cacheRead":88079,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":89836,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779537323349,"responseId":"0660c8b135b2f40708ed478631d2a8b7"}}
{"type":"message","id":"dd47ab28","parentId":"67392a5c","timestamp":"2026-05-23T12:00:00.065Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"user:ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b6e2d2570f4a0c377374dea449fd\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sat 2026-05-23 19:59 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\"\n}\n```\n\n1，对，2发过去无任何回复， 所有的agent都正常，只有这个没有回复。并且选品大师子在openclaw自身的webui后台 是可以回复的。"}],"timestamp":1779537599910}}
