{"type":"message","id":"552653fd","parentId":"77a362be","timestamp":"2026-05-23T12:00:15.313Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user confirms:\n1. They are messaging the correct TK bot in Feishu\n2. Messages go through with no reply at all\n3. All other agents work fine\n4. TK 选品大师 CAN reply in OpenClaw's own web UI backend\n\nThis is very interesting. The TK bot works in OpenClaw web UI, but when messages come from Feishu, they get no reply. This means the issue is with how Feishu routes messages to the tts account.\n\nThe fact that it works in OpenClaw web UI but not from Feishu strongly suggests the problem is with Feishu message routing to the tts account specifically, OR with how the tts account processes incoming Feishu messages vs web UI messages.\n\nSince all other agents work, the problem is likely specific to:\n1. The tts account's Feishu connection (webhook vs websocket)\n2. The tts account's allowFrom/dmPolicy not being correct\n3. The tts account's route configuration in OpenClaw\n\nWait - I just realized something. The user says \"选品大师子在openclaw自身的webui后台是可以回复的\" - this means when they use the OpenClaw web UI to chat with TK 选品大师, it works. This means the tts agent itself is working fine. The issue is specifically when messages come FROM Feishu to the TK bot.\n\nThis means the problem is at the Feishu -> OpenClaw routing layer for the tts account. The Feishu messages for the TK bot are not reaching OpenClaw, or if they do reach OpenClaw, they're not being routed to the tts agent.\n\nThis could be because:\n1. The TK bot (cli_a930f78f51399bc6) in Feishu is not properly configured to receive messages\n2. The TK bot's webhook is not set up correctly in Feishu\n\n\n3. The tts account's Feishu channel might be using webhook mode when it should be using websocket, or vice versa. The key difference between working agents and TK is likely the connectionMode setting for the tts account. In OpenClaw's config, I see feishu connectionMode is set to websocket at the top level, but the tts account configuration shows enabled: true with name: \"TK 选品大师\" - the account-level settings might be overriding the global ones, causing the tk bot's Feishu integration to fail while other agents work fine.\n","thinkingSignature":"b7b80671a5ba1d1c21033b5040479eca98c121fbaa641705c5f1ba22c43235e8"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n这个信息很关键——TK 选品大师 在 OpenClaw web UI 里能回复，说明 Agent 本身没问题，问题是**飞书消息进不来**。\n\n这说明问题出在 Feishu → OpenClaw 的路由层面，不是 Agent 本身。\n\n让我检查一下 TK bot 的飞书连接模式：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_z2zsumcnk0i9_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 -c \"\nimport json\nwith open('/home/halei/.openclaw/openclaw.json') as f:\n    cfg = json.load(f)\nfeishu = cfg['channels']['feishu']\ntts = feishu['accounts']['tts']\nkiit = feishu['accounts']['kiit']\n\nprint('=== 全局 Feishu 配置 ===')\nprint(f'connectionMode: {feishu.get(\\\"connectionMode\\\")}')\nprint(f'webhookPath: {feishu.get(\\\"webhookPath\\\")}')\nprint()\n\nprint('=== kiit account ===')\nprint(f'appId: {kiit[\\\"appId\\\"]}')\nprint(f'enabled: {kiit[\\\"enabled\\\"]}')\nprint(f'connectionMode: {kiit.get(\\\"connectionMode\\\", \\\"未设置（继承全局）\\\")}')\nprint(f'webhookPath: {kiit.get(\\\"webhookPath\\\", \\\"未设置（继承全局）\\\")}')\nprint()\n\nprint('=== tts account (TK 选品大师) ===')\nprint(f'appId: {tts[\\\"appId\\\"]}')\nprint(f'enabled: {tts[\\\"enabled\\\"]}')\nprint(f'connectionMode: {tts.get(\\\"connectionMode\\\", \\\"未设置（继承全局）\\\")}')\nprint(f'webhookPath: {tts.get(\\\"webhookPath\\\", \\\"未设置（继承全局）\\\")}')\nprint()\n\n# Check if there's websocket specifically for tts\naccount_ws = tts.get('connectionMode', feishu.get('connectionMode'))\nprint(f'TK bot 实际使用的 connectionMode: {account_ws}')\n\"","timeout":5}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":9003,"output":970,"cacheRead":80873,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":90846,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779537600393,"responseId":"0660c9c16ac33fb6cd5761264bedced4"}}
{"type":"message","id":"6c82d705","parentId":"552653fd","timestamp":"2026-05-23T12:00:15.610Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_z2zsumcnk0i9_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== 全局 Feishu 配置 ===\nconnectionMode: websocket\nwebhookPath: /feishu/events\n\n=== kiit account ===\nappId: cli_a93650c6fc785bce\nenabled: True\nconnectionMode: 未设置（继承全局）\nwebhookPath: 未设置（继承全局）\n\n=== tts account (TK 选品大师) ===\nappId: cli_a930f78f51399bc6\nenabled: True\nconnectionMode: 未设置（继承全局）\nwebhookPath: 未设置（继承全局）\n\nTK bot 实际使用的 connectionMode: websocket"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":58,"aggregated":"=== 全局 Feishu 配置 ===\nconnectionMode: websocket\nwebhookPath: /feishu/events\n\n=== kiit account ===\nappId: cli_a93650c6fc785bce\nenabled: True\nconnectionMode: 未设置（继承全局）\nwebhookPath: 未设置（继承全局）\n\n=== tts account (TK 选品大师) ===\nappId: cli_a930f78f51399bc6\nenabled: True\nconnectionMode: 未设置（继承全局）\nwebhookPath: 未设置（继承全局）\n\nTK bot 实际使用的 connectionMode: websocket","cwd":"/home/halei/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1779537615607}}
