{"type":"message","id":"605453a8","parentId":"d9efa20d","timestamp":"2026-05-23T12:14:24.168Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me think about this from first principles and try a different approach.\n\nThe user says:\n1. TK 选品大师 (tts) works in OpenClaw web UI ✅\n2. TK 选品大师 works via cron (9AM push) ✅\n3. TK 选品大师 does NOT work when sending messages directly via Feishu ❌\n4. All other agents work fine via Feishu ✅\n\nThis is a very specific failure mode. The tts bot's Feishu integration is not receiving or processing user messages.\n\nKey observations:\n- tts has its own dedicated Feishu app (`cli_a930f78f51399bc6`)\n- The app is enabled and configured (we can see it in the status screenshot)\n- The account is properly configured with allowFrom and dmPolicy\n- The bot worked before (May 22 cron ran successfully)\n\n\n- The Feishu app's webhook might not be properly registered or the long-polling connection for this specific bot could have dropped, even though both bots use websocket mode globally. Let me check the connection status directly.\n","thinkingSignature":"c300c87db23009d6a2f6c22476f7e1ed2290962986bee93c0660f9c69c1348c5"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ohd4r1ailw6h_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"journalctl -n 1000 --no-pager 2>/dev/null | grep -iE \"websocket|connected|disconnected|reconnecting|feed.*lark|lark.*feed\" | tail -30","timeout":5}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":97,"output":306,"cacheRead":99421,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":99824,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779538455673,"responseId":"0660cd1825a85ff6fd614dda58ae2e98"}}
