{"type":"message","id":"ee551d3e","parentId":"2f560a21","timestamp":"2026-05-23T12:20:31.843Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is saying that in Feishu, all bots are working (channel is working), but only TK选品大师 (tts) is not responding. This confirms the issue is specific to the tts bot.\n\nThe metadata shows this message is from `ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb` and it's going to kiit (since I'm responding now in kiit's session).\n\nBut the user says only TK doesn't work. This means:\n1. kiit (main) works\n2. tts (TK) doesn't work\n\nThis is really puzzling because tts is configured correctly. Let me think...\n\nThe message metadata shows it's from the user, but this conversation is with kiit. The user says in Feishu, all bots work except TK.\n\nWait - could the user be saying that all the OTHER agents (content, finance, etc.) work in Feishu, but TK doesn't? That would make more sense. The user said \"飞书里面所有的bot都通道\" - all bots in Feishu are working, only TK doesn't work. So messages to content agent → content agent works. Messages to finance agent → finance agent works. Messages to TK → TK doesn't work.\n\nThis would confirm TK's Feishu channel (its WebSocket connection to Feishu) is broken while the others are fine.\n\nBut wait - in the current kiit conversation, I'm responding to the user's message. So kiit IS working. And the other agents (content, finance, etc.) have their own separate Feishu accounts and should be working too.\n\nThe key question: does the user have OTHER agents' conversations working? If content agent, finance agent, etc. all respond to DMs in Feishu, but TK doesn't, then the issue is specifically with TK's Feishu app (cli_a930f78f51399bc6).\n\nActually, I should just ask the user for clarification. The phrasing \"飞书里面所有的bot都通道，只有tk选品大师\" is a bit ambiguous in Chinese. It could mean:\n\n\n1. \"All bots in Feishu work, only TK doesn't work\" (TK is broken, others are fine)\n2. \"All bots go through (the same channel), only TK选品大师 (doesn't respond)\"\n\nGiven the context of the conversation, I think the user means: messages to TK don't get responses, while messages to other bots DO work. This would confirm TK's Feishu WebSocket is disconnected while other accounts' connections remain active. Since all bots use the same feishu plugin in OpenClaw, the issue is isolated to TK's app configuration or its WebSocket connection to Feishu.\n\nLet me check the Feishu app status for TK. TK's WebSocket might be broken while other accounts' connections are fine. I need to verify TK's app credentials and event subscriptions in Feishu's developer console. Let me ask the user for clarification on whether other bots are responding, then check the configuration.\n","thinkingSignature":"c26177398864a477d7a3120f57e3cf3a0f1a551524828a3c1ba4bb37640a8bbf"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n明白了。TK 选品大师在飞书里的 WebSocket 接收有问题。\n\n**关键确认：** 你能试着给其他 agent（比如 content 或 finance）发一条消息，看看能收到回复吗？如果其他 agent 的飞书账号都正常，只有 TK 不行，说明问题出在 TK 选品大师这个飞书应用本身。\n\n可能的原因：\n1. TK 应用在飞书开放平台被停用或进入\"沙箱\"状态\n2. TK 的事件订阅（接收消息）被取消了\n3. TK 应用的机器人能力被意外关闭\n\n你能去飞书开放平台 → 找 TK 选品大师的应用 → 截个图给我看看\"应用状态\"和\"事件订阅\"那里是什么情况吗？\n\n或者我帮你远程看一下 tk 应用在飞书那边的状态？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":10612,"output":788,"cacheRead":59813,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":71213,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779538814549,"responseId":"0660ce7f7e9fb52f74fd30de6ef8c835"}}
