{"type":"message","id":"60228f10","parentId":"53490119","timestamp":"2026-05-23T13:03:56.242Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I can see the full config. The important thing I notice:\n\n1. The tts account is **MISSING** from the accounts list! Looking at the accounts:\n- kiit: appId=cli_a93650c6fc785bce\n- agent-orchestrator: appId=cli_a9558a1795799bb5\n- default: dmPolicy=pairing\n- content: appId=cli_a978060ba7249bd8\n- traffic: appId=cli_a9365703ce78dbb5\n- ops: appId=cli_a954f94ade79dbcd\n- director: appId=cli_a96d9bcb44b9dcba\n- finance: appId=cli_a96af4eceab99cb5\n- review: appId=cli_a954fb807f7adcd2\n- koc: appId=cli_a96af5b441f91bb5\n\n**There is NO \"tts\" account in the accounts list!** The user must have deleted it when they \"unbound\" it.\n\n2. The bindings list has 9 entries (main, agent-orchestrator, content, traffic, ops, director, finance, review, koc) but **NO tts binding**!\n\n3. The bindings that exist all have the correct routing - main→kiit, content→content, etc. But tts is missing.\n\nSo the user deleted the tts account configuration when they \"unbound\" it! Now I need to re-add it.\n\nThe user gave me:\n- appId: cli_a930f78f51399bc6\n- appSecret: sWYftqexDF2zr6I36ofoyhSz8rLxThbY\n\n\nI need to add back the tts account and binding. The account needs appId, appSecret, and enabled=true, and I should set connectionMode to websocket since the old config had that. I'll add the tts binding back to route feishu tts messages to the tts agent, then restart the gateway. the account configuration. The binding type defaults to \"route\" anyway, so the explicit \"type\": \"route\" isn't necessary.\n\nFor the account settings, I need to set `connectionMode: \"websocket\"` to ensure it's using websocket mode rather than webhook. Then I'll patch the config and restart to apply the changes.","thinkingSignature":"1627518aba0035f58a380367c5977457fbcf18faca84bdeecb9bf053d2abce89"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n找到了！**tts 账号被你解绑后，整个账号配置都没了**——openclaw.json 里的 `channels.feishu.accounts.tts` 不存在了，bindings 里也没有 tts 的路由。\n\n我现在把它重新加回来：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_psfnb753797o_1","name":"gateway","arguments":{"action":"config.patch","note":"重新添加 TK 选品大师 (tts) 飞书账号配置，并绑定到 tts agent","path":"channels/feishu/accounts/tts","raw":"{\"enabled\": true, \"appId\": \"cli_a930f78f51399bc6\", \"appSecret\": \"sWYftq…ThbY\", \"connectionMode\": \"websocket\"}"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":3936,"output":691,"cacheRead":94912,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":99539,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779541428390,"responseId":"0660d8b4f1e859fb6b38df5738990ae0"}}
