{"type":"message","id":"dc0ba705","parentId":"f606b948","timestamp":"2026-05-23T13:55:01.688Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see the issue now! The kiit agent session (`agent:main:feishu:kiit:direct:ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb`, sessionId `405b68a9-c988-46c4-9527-0873f7b2008e`) is STALLED! It was processing for 693 seconds (~11.5 minutes!) with `activeWorkKind=model_call` and `lastProgress=model_call:started`. \n\nThe diagnostic shows:- \"stalled session\" at 21:48:51 (age=693s, state=processing)\n- \"long-running session\" at 21:53:22 (age=148s, state=processing, reason=queued_behind_active_work)\n\n\nThe kiit agent got stuck waiting for the MiniMax model to respond, so messages just kept piling up in the queue while kiit was hung on that same model call. Once the session finally recovered, it sent 2 replies and immediately received and dispatched the new message. The root cause is that the model call to MiniMax is taking way too long or timing out.\n\nBut here's the thing—the user sent \"通信测试\" from WeChat at 21:49, and even though kiit eventually responded with \"搞定了！✅\", they never saw the reply in the Feishu TK bot chat because that message came through a different channel. The kiit session is the one that's stalled, not the tts session.\n\nLooking at the timeline more carefully, at 21:36 the user sent the message that triggered kiit's long-running session, and since then every message they sent got queued up as kiit stayed stuck on that model call. The kiit session started processing around 21:37 and has been running for about 11 minutes straight. Meanwhile, the tts agent never got any messages routed to it—the user was probably sending to the TK bot, but those messages went to the wrong account instead.\n\nI need to figure out why the TK bot messages aren't reaching the tts agent in the first place. Let me look at the routing logs around 21:36-21:37 to see if the messages even got routed to tts when they came in.\n","thinkingSignature":"2b794338472f64172c1eca074ca273823aa0f343a721d1401fad2cc0a8fcb932"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_1b2jrtu8cd75_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"journalctl -n 500 --no-pager 2>/dev/null | grep -E \"21:3[6-7]\" | grep -iE \"feishu|tts|kiit|dispatch\" | head -30","timeout":5}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":529,"output":548,"cacheRead":77856,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":78933,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779544490592,"responseId":"0660e4ab40fe7e170c7a164bcdc7f332"}}
